sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant UI as OtaManagement / dashboard
  participant API as Fastify REST API
  participant Command as CommandService
  participant Audit as AuditService
  participant Repo as Command repository
  participant Gateway as SocketIoGateway
  participant Device as Sensor device

  UI->>API: POST /api/ota/upload-bin
  API-->>UI: Firmware URL under /ota-bins
  UI->>API: POST /api/ota/dispatch with deviceIds + otaUrl
  API->>Command: Create OTA command per target device
  Command->>Repo: Save pending command
  API->>Gateway: dispatch device:command
  Gateway-->>Device: device:command
  Device-->>Gateway: device:command:ack
  Gateway->>Command: Update ack/result status
  Gateway-->>UI: device:ack / device:command update
  API->>Audit: Record ota_dispatch summary
  UI->>API: GET /api/commands/recent or lookup
  API-->>UI: Command status list
